1. *Vašoj* porodici želim sreću i uspeh. (I wish your family luck and success.)
2. On je poklonio knjigu *vašoj* majci. (He gave a book to your mother.)
3. Danas će biti lep dan, to je *vašoj* sreći. (Today will be a beautiful day, that's your luck.)
4. Ovi izazovi su *vašoj* disciplini. (These challenges are your discipline.)
5. *Vašoj* deci ću dati najbolje školske knjige. (I will give your children the best school books.)